<h1 style="font-size:clamp(24px,4vw,38px);font-weight:400;color:#fff;margin:16px 0;line-height:1.2;">Samsung Galaxy Ring vs Oura Ring 4: which one to buy for your needs</h1>
<p style="font-size:17px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.55);margin-bottom:8px;">The two best smart rings on the market head to head. Different price, different ecosystem, different business model. We explain exactly which one is right for you.</p>
<div style="font-size:11px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.3);font-family:monospace;margin-bottom:28px;">📅 May 2026 · ⏱ 10 min read</div>
<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1576566588028-4147f3842f27?w=800&q=80" alt="Smart ring comparison" style="width:100%;border-radius:12px;aspect-ratio:16/9;object-fit:cover;margin-bottom:28px;" loading="lazy"/>
<div class="verdict-box">
  <span class="verdict-box__label">⚡ QUICK VERDICT</span>
  <p>Choose the Oura Ring 4 if you have an iPhone or prioritize maximum accuracy in sleep and HRV. Choose the Samsung Galaxy Ring if you use Android, already have Samsung products, or don't want to pay a monthly subscription.</p>
</div>
<div class="article-content">
<h2>Head-to-head comparison</h2>
